@EU_Commission 
#intled #Mobility 
Opening of the annual #NARIC meeting in Brussels, Belgium. +40 participants from many signatory States to Lisbon #recognition Convention (LRC) are here.

@EU_Commission Nice to see this happening! just regret we're not 20 any more... and one other thing, do you really need 1500 words to explain:
1⃣You need to be 18 and EU citizen
2⃣A quiz and subsidiary question will decide between the successful applicants
